You have the right to (1) request to know more about and access your personal data, including in a portable format, (2) request deletion of your personal data, and (3) request correction of inaccurate personal data To request access, correction, or deletion of your personal data, please submit your request through this or call our toll‑free number at 1 858 345 1444. Once we receive the request, we will verify your request. Event registrants and attendees may update their user profiles for Events we host by logging into the applicable event website or registration page.
